claim: Tim Kaine worked as the chief commander of the Commonwealth of Virginia.
premise_source_doc_sentence: As Treasurer of Virginia under Governor Kaine and Secretary of Finance Jody Wagner , Powell serves on the following boards and authorities , the first six being staffed by the Department of the Treasury : Commonwealth of Virginia Treasury Board , Debt Capacity Advisory Committee , Virginia College Building Authority , Virginia Public Building Authority , Virginia Public School Authority , Tobacco Settlement Financing Corporation , Virginia College Savings Plan , Virginia Housing Development Authority , Virginia Port Authority , Virginia Resources Authority and the Virginia Small Business Financing Authority .
